Image-2024-12-04-at-23.56.36-175x300.jpeg 175w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.56.36-768x1317.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.56.36-896x1536.jpeg 896w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.56.36-262x450.jpeg 262w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.56.36.jpeg 933w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 597px) 100vw, 597px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0be0fcb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0be0fcb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90bd4c7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"90bd4c7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5423e9c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5423e9c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary<\/h3>\n<p><b>Morning Pick-Up:<br><\/b>Your day begins with a comfortable pick-up from your riad or hotel in Marrakech. Enjoy the scenic drive through the Moroccan countryside, with opportunities to stop and see the famous argan tree goats and visit a local argan oil cooperative run by Berber women.<\/p>\n<p><b>Explore Essaouira:<br><\/b>Upon arrival in Essaouira, you\u2019ll have time to explore this charming seaside town at your own pace. Wander through the medina&#8217;s narrow streets, lined with artisan shops, galleries, and traditional souks.<\/p>\n<p><b>Visit the Port and Ramparts:<br><\/b>Head to the vibrant fishing port to watch fishermen bring in their daily catch. Stroll along the impressive ramparts, which offer stunning views of the ocean and the city\u2019s historic architecture.<\/p>\n<p><b>Enjoy Fresh Seafood:<br><\/b>For lunch, indulge in freshly caught seafood at one of the many restaurants overlooking the harbor. From grilled fish to traditional Moroccan tajines, Essaouira offers a culinary experience you won\u2019t forget.<\/p>\n<p><b>Relax by the Beach:<br><\/b>Take a leisurely walk along the sandy beach or simply relax while enjoying the refreshing ocean breeze.<\/p>\n<p><b>Return to Marrakech:<br><\/b>In the late afternoon, your driver will take you back to Marrakech, ensuring a comfortable and relaxing end to your day.<\/p>\n<p><b>Highlights:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Discover the rich history and culture of Essaouira, a UNESCO World Heritage site.<\/p>\n<p>Enjoy fresh seafood and local Moroccan dishes by the ocean.<\/p>\n<p>Visit the medina, fishing port, and historic ramparts.<\/p>\n<p>Relax on the beautiful beach and soak in the coastal atmosphere.<\/p>\n<p>Scenic drive through the Moroccan countryside with stops along the way.<\/p>\n<p>Essaouira is the perfect destination for a relaxing day trip, offering a unique mix of culture, history, and natural beauty. Let us take you on this unforgettable journey!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Day Trip to Essaouira from Marrakech Discover the charm of Essaouira, a picturesque coastal city located just a few hours from Marrakech. Known as the &#8220;Pearl of the Atlantic,&#8221; Essaouira is a UNESCO World Heritage site offering a perfect blend of history, culture, and breathtaking ocean views. Itinerary Morning Pick-Up:Your day begins with a comfortable [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11313,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11686","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11686","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11686"}],"version-history":[{"count":29,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11686\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12788,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11686\/revisions\/12788"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11313"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11686"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}